overview: Yep, Chad's back. And his many fans deserve a lot better than this. Conners is so massively pumped these days that he moves awkwardly and has lost a real sense of aesthetic beauty. In addition, some of the sex is obviously faked, and director T.J. Paris relies too often on slow-motion and looped footage. Fans of muscled studs will find Conners, Rob Steel and Chance Caldwell easy on the eyes, but otherwise, Chad's Back is a real disappointment.
title: Chad's Back: In the Gym
